{"tid":1251361,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[E3采訪] 宮崎英高：真實的世界是一片荒漠 光明在黑暗中更加迷人","createTime":"2019-06-22T13:19:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T10:07:04.000Z","uid":75050,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"13f0259caeb2ce46c759e85ea3c18f7627f7faff","tid":1251361,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T13:19:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Nmia.Gaming/posts/1270530239781518\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNmia.Gaming%2Fposts%2F1270530239781518&d=ahpQ5aMQEo4h8Mt%2B3j6t3vSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=91c5ed33\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Nmia.Gaming/posts/1270530239781518</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>【宮崎英高：真實的世界是一片荒漠 光明在黑暗中更加迷人】</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4OpRTO8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4OpRTO8.jpg&h=9e5d7cd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nIGN今日公布了E3期間對宮崎英高的完整采訪，他在其中談到了自己在世界觀設定方面的看法：「<strong><ins>對我而言，充滿光明和快樂的世界反而顯得不太真實。</ins></strong>這聽起來像是心理創傷的表現，但我的確認為世界對人們而言就是一片荒漠，這就是我看待它的方式。」<br />\n<br />\n不過這樣的設定在遊戲裡的藝術性上卻能帶來獨到的效果：「光明在黑暗中才會顯得更加迷人，<strong><ins>當你在廢墟中看到美麗的事物時，你也對它更加珍惜。</ins></strong>當你擁有一堆寶石的時候，或許不會對其中某顆太過看重。但是如果這顆寶石是在泥濘中找到的，那麼它的價值會變得高出許多。」<br />\n<br />\n此外宮崎英高還談到了喬治&middot;R&middot;R&middot;馬丁在遊戲中的具體參與方式，後者將會塑造《Elden Ring》的神話背景而<strong><ins>劇情方面則是由宮崎英高本人操刀</ins></strong>，因為他不想對馬丁的創意進行任何限制。<br />\n<br />\n「至少從FromSoftware以往的經驗來看，遊戲的敘事方式往往會給作者帶來很多限制，而我不想把這樣的限制施加到馬丁身上。它所描繪的那個時代玩家並不會直接參與，所以也就能自由自在地進行創作了。我們也不想讓《Elden Ring》成為一款故事驅動的線性遊戲，上述的問題都能通過讓馬丁負責世界構架來解決。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ccj2Hy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ccj2Hy.jpg&h=9e162174&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource：<a href=\"https://gematsu.com/2019/06/elden-ring-is-an-evolution-of-dark-souls-says-director-hidetaka-miyazaki\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgematsu.com%2F2019%2F06%2Felden-ring-is-an-evolution-of-dark-souls-says-director-hidetaka-miyazaki&d=ahpQ5aMQEo4h8Mt%2B3j6t3vSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=2caa3cf6\" target=\"_blank\">https://gematsu.com/2019/06/elden-ring-is-an-evolution-of-dark-souls-says-director-hidetaka-miyazaki</a>"},{"pid":"1db596fb5fea26a70dd478fba7af5ea87a92bd26","tid":1251361,"uid":75050,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T13:20:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ibREigA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FibREigA.jpg&h=9e02db3e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b22f0220c5f895a9b3c6e853f85ba799417a799","tid":1251361,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T14:26:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98a3c02fa3cb5527d0108eff20311885eea7336f","tid":1251361,"uid":25367,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T14:41:15.000Z","msg":"肯出armored core未"},{"pid":"733008214e1fee8fe8e86dcd342ef73d70b521fc","tid":1251361,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T22:00:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a0d3f1e0e8770a5d37c769c503ce8d78c547d9a","tid":1251361,"uid":256837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T01:29:14.000Z","msg":"好想要不幫2"},{"pid":"5974970261ee00763941ad5bdd8716552e2ac98d","tid":1251361,"uid":90259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98a3c02fa3cb5527d0108eff20311885eea7336f","tid":1251361,"uid":25367,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T14:41:15.000Z","msg":"肯出armored core未"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T06:11:56.000Z","msg":"宮崎：賺咁少，不了"},{"pid":"6c708f7d81eadc58d323f9427bd6b2127662dd17","tid":1251361,"uid":25345,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T06:14:39.000Z","msg":"佢本身既靈魂就係dark soul<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=